Author: Warrantoken
Title: [ANN] [Warrantoken] | Securing Property Rights for People Everywhere
Body: Warrantoken.com  Discord | Telegram | Mailing List | Reddit | Github | YouTube | Twitter | Technical Whitepaper   Automating & Securing Proof of Purchase on the Blockchain The first global business application for blockchain technology, based on a live blockchain platform and mobile app.   Business Benefits Eliminate Billions in fraud & Trillions in customer relations costs using automated & secure Blockchain records to easily manage product warranties.  Customer Benefits Register & transfer warranty instantly with a simple QR scan. No receipts, serial numbers or Blockchain knowledge required. Receive WTK Tokens as a reward.  Platform Goal The goal of the Warrantoken platform is ubiquitous adoption in the retail industry, leading Warrantoken and WTK Tokens to be introduced to hundreds of millions becoming the most widely used crypto asset.  Value Proposition Hundreds of millions of people will be first exposed to crypto assets through our easy to use mobile app, when they open a product and find a Warrantoken QR Code. When they scan their first item they may be rewarded with free WTK tokens by the generosity of UNIVEC FOUNDATION. The "network effect" is thought by many to be the underlying value proposition of all digital assets, and by making WTK the worlds most widely used crypto-asset it will have the largest "network effect".    Download Our App               Brought to you by: UNIVEC FOUNDATION  UNIVEC FOUNDATION works with Technology and Media partners listed below to develop digital solutions powering the future economy.           UNIVEC, INC. (Universal E-Commerce) is an American E-Commerce powerhouse since 1993 with Manhattan offices at 1 Rockefeller Plaza, New York. UNIVEC, INC. invented and created the first original E-Commerce protocol in the world, and UNIVEC INC.'s protocol was used by United States Department of Defense, NASA and The World Bank for complete E-Commerce procedures globally. UNIVEC INC. has experience developing mobile E-Commerce applications to power the digital economy of the future, including the latest public apps produced by UNIVEC, INC. which are currently on the market in production in Europe and Asia. UNIVEC INC. has partnered with UNIVEC FOUNDATION to handle software development, including mobile applications, blockchain-based smart contracts, web development and technical support among others. UNIVEC INC. has allocated its elite 1 Rockefeller-based development team to develop and support on the Warrantoken platform.  AMRICA ENTERTAINMENT is an American media agency with global offices in Europe/Asia and North America. Amrica is one of the largest and most innovative independent media agencies with deep connections on the east coast US and in the "Eurasia" market. Amrica has partnered with UNIVEC FOUNDATION to handle global business development and media management for the Warrantoken platform.  Please visit the respective websites to learn more about the UNIVEC FOUNDATION and its partners.
